WEBVTT

00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:33.920
in using Sahel land for agriculture.

00:13:35.840 --> 00:13:37.040
More benefits,

00:13:37.880 --> 00:13:39.160
higher employment,

00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:44.080
climate change mitigation
by reversing desertification

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:46.920
and greater food security.

00:13:47.680 --> 00:13:49.040
Nice vision, right?

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:52.280
Well, we are working
towards getting it done.

00:13:53.240 --> 00:13:57.496
Last month we introduced fonio
to shoppers in New York City

00:13:57.520 --> 00:13:58.736
and online,

00:13:58.760 --> 00:14:04.416
in a package that makes it attractive
and desirable and accessible.